* Enter Gun Time for 5k Race Prompt
*   When to use:    Just once at the starting gun.
*   How to use:     Double-click to open the dialog box, then enter your time (using the HH:MM:SS.00 format).
*   Alternative:    Feel free to edit the input directly within the GunTime file, then double-click to run it!


select              Race
=                   5k
selected            GunStart
selected Message    ?ENTER Gun Time and click OK Format MUST BE HH:MM:SS.ss
